from their company.

96
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,720
Something like... Xi?

97
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,189
Mu Chenxi.

98
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,120
Yeah.

99
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,669
Yes, that's her.

100
00:07:12,670 --> 00:07:13,920
Her again.

101
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:16,909
Minister Cheng,

102
00:07:16,910 --> 00:07:18,469
when are we shooting the promo video

103
00:07:18,470 --> 00:07:19,229
for our drama?

104
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:21,680
There's no schedule for it yet.

105
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:24,669
But my upcoming schedule is packed.

106
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:26,880
If I'm going to film a duo promo,
it has to be today.

107
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,960
All right, Miss.

108
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:30,160
Well...

109
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:31,680
I'll arrange it.

110
00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:33,080
It's just that...

111
00:07:33,150 --> 00:07:35,280
Zhiqing has an event this afternoon.

112
00:07:36,030 --> 00:07:37,200
That's fine.

113
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:40,240
I can film
with our drama's second male lead first.

114
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:44,640
Look at the camera.

115
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,480
Good.

116
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,000
Very good.

117
00:07:49,550 --> 00:07:50,880
Great, move to the side.

118
00:07:54,470 --> 00:07:56,560
