119
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,240
Yes.

120
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:01,680
That's perfect.

121
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,829
Good, very good.

122
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,800
All right, you two can go change now.

123
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:08,389
Thanks for the hard work, Lidong.

124
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,800
