128
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:17,269
My sister and I tried it last time.

129
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,429
The food was really good.

130
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,669
If you're free after this,

131
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:21,280
